data.name: One Line Task :  Choose List !! Part(1/2)
data.description:
Given n>0 from one of this lists 

                                       ...5,10,15,20,25...  list 1
                                       ...6,11,16,21,26...  list 2
                                       ...7,12,17,22,27...  list 3
                                       ...8,13,18,23,28...  list 4
                                       ...9,14,19,24,29...  list 5
Write a function that return the list number which contain the given number.

Example : 
 
          n=8  return 4
          n=1  return 2

Your code should be less than 12 charcter !
                                        
Part 2 : https://www.codewars.com/kata/5a88a9b160c8132eb2002239/train
